The paper proposes a novel attention mechanism for forecasting multivariate time series data using recurrent neural networks. This falls under the domain of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.NE. The proposed model also involves the use of filters to extract temporal patterns, which is similar to signal processing techniques used in computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the paper could also be relevant to the sub-categories cs.CV and cs.CL.
